{
  "3292590": {
    "name": "Donerksela -Sacred Area-",
    "steam_appid": 3292590,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292590/extras/7b746a8fd91b86ca60d2ccb722e95a4f.avif?t=1733929238\" width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >&quot;Donerksela Sacred Area&quot; is Turn based simulation game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are the Candidate God and Guardian on a certain place, fight the attacking enemy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game's goal is defeat strong Bosses and become the God, through the &quot;produce resource&quot;, &quot;enhance build&quot; and more.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292590/extras/708ccb7de55f621790825180501b289d.avif?t=1733929238\" width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Main character (Fatima) is able to Growing if certain conditions are met!!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Growing can gain more powerful, that be advantageous about game progress.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In addition, Sometimes transform appearance for more sacred or evil.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Of course, each appearance has its own appearance at different age!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292590/extras/65ab5f5f2f0f22d0bf9447a54595476c.avif?t=1733929238\" width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enhance by Study(research) that spend the resource.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And exists Passive Item that exert various effects.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enhance ally side utilize every element.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Maybe you can defeat Boss in one blow.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292590/extras/2fef6683be9fa0b1212cbca3403f4cae.avif?t=1733929238\" width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As a loop element, able to freely make the game easier or harder (to some extent).</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And you can check past statistical information and achievement!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game unfolds differently each time, so you can play it multiple times.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >(There are also 2x and 4x speed modes to help you play multiple times!)</p>",
